McGettigan’s Irish pub is spreading its wings…we are opening another outlet in Abu Dhabi shortly…
Do you have what it takes to work in one of the busiest bars in Abu Dhabi and are still able to brighten up people’s faces with your infectious smile?
If you are energetic and committed and want to work in a fun environment, McGettigan’s is the place for you.
Salary & Benefits:
This position offers a highly competitive salary and package which includes Basic salary, accommodation, transport, duty meals, air ticket and medical insurance.
